<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div xml:id="Aink109">
      <lg type="edition">
<l>aṉṉai vāḻivēṇ ṭaṉṉai neyta</l>
<l>ṉīrppaṭar tūmpiṉ pūkkeḻu tuṟaiva</l>
<l>ṉentō ṭuṟanta kālai yevaṉkol</l>
<l>paṉṉāḷ varumava ṉaḷitta poḻutē</l>
</lg>
<lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>  Oh mother, please mother,</l>
<l>When the man of the harbour with flowers</l>
<l>Of Neytal with tubes (=stamen) that spread upon the water</l>
<l>Abandoned my shoulders,</l>
<l>What will come for many days? -- </l>
<l>[Thoughts of] those days when he was generous?!</l>
</lg>
    </div>
